# 3. Find Intersection of Three Tuples

## Problem

Find common elements present in all three tuples.

### Example

```python
t1 = (1, 2, 3, 4)
t2 = (2, 3, 5)
t3 = (2, 3, 6)
```

### Output

```python
2
3
```

## Built-in Solution

```python
t1 = (1, 2, 3, 4)
t2 = (2, 3, 5)
t3 = (2, 3, 6)

result = set(t1) & set(t2) & set(t3)

print(result)
```

## Pure Logic Solution

```python
t1 = (1, 2, 3, 4)
t2 = (2, 3, 5)
t3 = (2, 3, 6)

for num in t1:

    if num in t2 and num in t3:
        print(num)
```

